platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: From indie developer Evan Kice, Afterplace is an unforgettable RPG lovingly crafted for mobile, forgoing virtual buttons in favor of swipes and taps to control its precise combat. The game is also just a delight to explore, brimming with surprises ranging from sarcastic vending machines to nightmarish bosses. Even after two playthroughs, we’re still finding new paths, new choices, and unexpected encounters that make us laugh.
A delight to explore, brimming with surprises ranging from sarcastic vending machines to nightmarish bosses, we’re still finding new paths, new choices, and unexpected encounters that make us laugh.
在這款充滿驚喜的探索遊戲中，你會遇到諷刺的自動販賣機、可怕的頭目，以及歡笑不斷的意外相遇。
Un jeu rempli de surprises, des distributeurs automatiques sarcastiques aux boss cauchemardesques. On trouve sans cesse de nouveaux passages, choix et personnages inopinés.
探索的樂趣在於各式各樣的驚喜，無論是尖酸刻薄的自動販賣機，還是可怕的老闆，我們仍在尋找新道路、新選擇和讓我們開懷大笑的意外遭遇。
A delight to explore, brimming with surprises ranging from sarcastic vending machines to nightmarish bosses, we’re still finding new paths, new choices and unexpected encounters that make us laugh.
皮肉たっぷりの自動販売機から悪夢のようなボスまで、驚きに満ちたアドベンチャーゲームです。ユーモアあふれる、新しい道、新しい選択肢、予期せぬ出会いが待ち受けています。
